{
  "stem": "1415.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I got up to sing, and I finished, and they started applauding, but the minute they saw her, everybody stopped.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I looked around, and I said, uh-oh, that's it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, in the meantime, she started applauding, so everybody joined in, and she asked me to come into her room afterwards.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to her room, and I became privileged, very privileged.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got extra food, and she asked me to-- to sing for her and her assistant.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it seems in the block, there was a-- a block eldester, and an assistant block eldester.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had a room all their own at the-- at the beginning of the block, which was right where that chimney went up, just before.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It had-- it had a room, and they had their own bunks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she asked me if I could come into her room, and I could sing to them, and if I know any songs-- any other songs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after all, I had two sisters, and they were already 18 and 16 at the time when they were taken away, so I heard a lot of love songs, even though we were a religious family at home.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they knew a lot of Polish love songs, and I-- like, I was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I really absorbed everything, and I learned their songs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I said, sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after that, I used to go into their room, and I would sing to them, and I would get little crumbs, little food, extra food.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would bring it back for my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was very privileged.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
